void AbstractSmsApp::OnSimSmsReady (   )  [protected, virtual]
 

The OnSimSmsReady-methods is triggered by a Stack Signal and is responsible to initialize Sms Handling. The SmsApplication will be registered to load Sms from Sim and FFS. It will be told to react on Messages, such as if a new message has been arrived.
